definition: many/much/often/a lot of/numerous/more/in excess/how (to what extent)/multi-/Taiwan pr. [duo2] when it means "how"
many/much/often/a lot of/numerous/more/in excess/how (to what extent)/multi-/Taiwan pr. [duo2] when it means "how"

sentences.english: This is just one of the many diverse ways that fluidised beds have been used.
sentences.chinese: 这只不过是流化床多种多样实际应用中的一种。

sentences.english: The beauty of silver brooches is that they come in a wide variety of styles.
sentences.chinese: 在美银胸针是，他们来到了多种多样的风格。

sentences.english: There's Milton. There are a number of possibilities.
sentences.chinese: 还有弥尔顿的推测，多种多样的可能性。

sentences.english: Our planet is rich in language diversity.
sentences.chinese: 我们星球上的语言多种多样，估计达六七千种。

sentences.english: There are also various cooking methods with local ethnic characteristics.
sentences.chinese: 烹饪的方法也是多种多样的，颇具地方民族特色。

sentences.english: We should differ it from the same language region because there are so many forms of reference objects to words.
sentences.chinese: 参照体是多种多样的，应当把它同论域等区别开来。

sentences.english: Various types of political committees are registered with the FEC.
sentences.chinese: 在联邦选举委员会登记的政治委员会多种多样。

sentences.english: The forms are unusual and embellished with ornaments and apparatuses.
sentences.chinese: 虫卵的形式多种多样，通常还会附加各种装饰和装置。

sentences.english: There are various ways to pay state tax.
sentences.chinese: 国家税的上缴方式多种多样。

sentences.english: The types of data which geologists collect are quite varied and numerous.
sentences.chinese: 地质学家所收集的资料是多种多样的并且数量很大。

sentences.english: The kinds of diseases of the turnout zone are multifarious.
sentences.chinese: 道岔区内病害形式多种多样。

sentences.english: The moves in chess are not only manifold, but involute.
sentences.chinese: 下棋的走法不但多种多样，而且错综复杂。

sentences.english: The etiquettes of the Tibetan people are omnipresent and diversified.
sentences.chinese: 礼仪在藏民族生活中无时无处不在，其形式多种多样。

sentences.english: The semantic relationships in modification-center structures are various.
sentences.chinese: 偏正结构内部的语义关系多种多样。

sentences.english: The benefits of easier surveillance are manifold.
sentences.chinese: 监视更为方便的好处多种多样。

sentences.english: Prophecy in the form of the time rumors are also varied.
sentences.chinese: 其时谶谣的形式也是多种多样的。
